	- new -E "set cdrom speed" option (Matthias Oster <Matthias.Oster@eikon.tum.de>)
	- new -R and -U "(un)register hwif" options (Christian Lademann <cal@zls.de>)
	- new contrib subdirectory with contributed scripts from users.
